subtitleNullable: RSS feed of BBC Burmese news, auto updating daily
descriptionNullable:
This dataset is to store the rss feed of BBC Burmese news. It includes the news title and short description. 

The good thing about BBC's short descriptions is they make it full sentence unlike other Burmese news.

Read more about BBC Burmese News RSS [here](https://www.bbc.com/burmese/help/2010/01/000000_rss_help)
